{"word":"τιθηνέομαι","slug":"τιθηνέομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>τιθηνέομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to nurse, suckle, tend as nurse</i>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to keep up, maintain</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}